(324, 1, 66, '<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25px; widows: 1; text-align: center;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;"><img alt="" src="http://www.cecac.cn/caee/u/cms/caee/201704/241701473n7f.jpg" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border: none; width: 600px; height: 802px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25px; widows: 1; text-align: center;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;">茅老师和</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;">许渊冲教授</span><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;">在一起</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25px; widows: 1; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">茅倬蕤</strong>，男，1983年4月出生，江西新余人，硕士学历，现任中国电子商务协会推进中心教育培训部主任，中国民主同盟盟员。英语教研及教学专家，国内“大电影英语教学第一人“及 ”“中英诗歌译诵/译唱第一人”，师从有“诗译英法唯一人”之称的许渊冲教授；北京外国语大学对外汉语访问学者；北京奥组委&amp;海淀区教委指定奥运英语初中组唯一官方培训师，全国基础英语素质教育实验基地研究员&amp;海淀区英语教研员；曾获北京市级、海淀区级公开课一等奖；北京市海淀区青年教师基本功大赛一等奖；国家级课程外研社和北京外国语大学联合颁发《典范英语》公开课一等奖；“十一五”教育部重点课题优质论文一等奖；北大附中校本教材主编；曾任职于北大附中，清华附中，12年一线教学和教师培训管理工作经验，在名师优质课上录制教学视频三十余部，出版教材十余部。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;"><strong style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">主要作品</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25px; widows: 1; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;">《英语情境发散式阅读：中考篇》出版社：中国计量出版；ISBN:9787502630799;2010年7月</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;">《写霸-中考作文178篇》出版社：浙江工商大学出版社；ISBN:9787-5178-0234-1;2014年3月</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;">《写霸-高考考作文178篇》出版社：浙江工商大学出版社；ISBN:9787-5178-0233-4;2014年3月</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25px; widows: 1;"><span style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; font-family: &quot;times new roman&quot;, times, serif;">疯狂英语---《中考语法直通车》出版社：中山大学出版社；ISBN:978-7-306-04998-8;2015年4月</span></p><div><br/></div>', '', '茅倬蕤'),
(354, 1, 81, '<p style="padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 2em;">7月29日，由中国互联网协会主办、北京博导前程信息技术有限公司承办的2014第七届中国网络营销大会在京举行。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; widows: 1;">&nbsp;</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 2em;">中国互联网协会副理事长高新民到会并作开幕演讲。他提出，国内网络营销日益趋向多样化，对整个互联网发展而言，院校实践人才的培养不足以满足 行业需求，院校需要高度关注流通领域电子商务和网络营销人才培养，同时要将网络营销人才的培养延伸到整个产业链。他强调，网络强国关键在于人才， 需要更多可靠的网络安全技术、网络营销人才。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; widows: 1;">&nbsp;</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 2em;">演讲中，高新民副理事长还针对当前电子商务的现状进行了分析，他指出，国内网络营销的规模从交易额上来讲已经超过美国等国家，但就网络营销对 传统行业的影响来看，我们还与欧美国家相距甚远。因此需要我们真切关注网络营销在流通中的作用，深入推进产业链的发展。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; widows: 1;">&nbsp;</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 2em;">自2001年加入IBM全球供应链领袖计划以来,丁先生历任美国战略外包及业务转型外包投标主管, IBM战略寻源项目办公室全球运营经理,美洲区供应链战略转型及流程外包资深经理，亚太区服务采购总监等。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; widows: 1;">&nbsp;</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 2em;">大会现场，中国网络营销领域最具市场价值的网络营销奖项——&quot;今典奖&quot;评选结果也一一揭晓，数十家企业与个人获得殊荣。</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: 25px; white-space: normal; widows: 1;">&nbsp;</p><p style="padding: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1; line-height: 22px; text-indent: 2em;">作为业内最具影响力和权威性的网络营销盛会，从2008年至今，中国网络营销大会已经成功举办六届。</p><p><br/></p>', '', ''),
(325, 1, 78, '<p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: normal; widows: 1;">·<span class="Apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></span><a href="http://www.cecac.cn/caee/examAddrDetail.jspx?id=1" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-decoration-line: none; font-family: 宋体; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: normal; white-space: normal; widows: 1;">北京市通信行业协会</a></p>', '', ''),
(326, 1, 78, '<p><a href="http://www.cecac.cn/caee/examAddrList.jspx?provId=22" target="_blank" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px; color: rgb(0, 51, 153); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; line-height: normal; text-align: -webkit-center; white-space: normal; widows: 1;">重庆</a></p>', '', ''),
